<view class="page">
  <view class="toolbar">
    <view class="segmented">
      <view class="seg-btn {{gender === 'male' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-gender="male" bindtap="onGenderTap">
        男性
      </view>
      <view class="seg-btn {{gender === 'female' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-gender="female" bindtap="onGenderTap">
        女性
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="segmented">
      <view class="seg-btn {{phase === 'bulk' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-phase="bulk" bindtap="onPhaseTap">
        增肌
      </view>
      <view class="seg-btn {{phase === 'cut' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-phase="cut" bindtap="onPhaseTap">
        减脂
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <scroll-view scroll-y scroll-x class="table-wrap">
    <view class="table">
      <view class="row header">
        <view class="cell head">体重\身高</view>
        <view class="cell head" wx:for="{{heights}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}cm</view>
      </view>

      <view class="row" wx:for="{{rows}}" wx:for-item="row" wx:key="weight">
        <view class="cell head">{{row.weight}}kg</view>
        <view class="cell"
              wx:for="{{row.cells}}"
              wx:for-item="cell"
              wx:key="height"
              bindtap="onCellTap"
              data-weight="{{row.weight}}"
              data-height="{{cell.height}}">
          <view wx:if="{{cell.value}}">
            <view class="line1">{{cell.text}}</view>
            <view class="line2">训/休/蛋</view>
          </view>
          <view wx:else class="empty">-</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="hint">
    每格三个数字分别是：训练日碳水 / 休息日碳水 / 每日蛋白（g/kg 体重）。点击某个格子将把对应倍率写入首页“基础配置”，并设置默认脂肪目标。
    <view style="margin-top:8rpx;color:#888;">来源：B 站「好人松松」</view>
  </view>
</view>

